  "id": "RAW_16bec442",
  "title": "微软 GigaTIME 登上《Cell》：5 美元切片变成免疫图谱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652654369&idx=3&sn=e6509af654c750413c46e873b25107fd",
  "date": "2025-12-13 09:03:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169362\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtx0EA7eJhEhzFsCHibRfmmpJJD7ibeq0xBLkmE9yKcdIdUrYbMoKUtAaaA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cff8c46a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtx0EA7eJhEhzFsCHibRfmmpJJD7ibeq0xBLkmE9yKcdIdUrYbMoKUtAaaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">微软在《Cell》公布了最新成果：GigaTIME能把一张H&amp;E切片翻译成过去稀缺的免疫图谱，并在人群尺度重建TIME。癌症免疫研究的许多旧限制，也因此开始松动。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你很难想象，一张医院里5美元的H&amp;E切片，有一天会被放到《Cell》上，甚至让微软CEO亲自站出来转发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169364\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5957446808510638\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1128\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1128\" data-height=\"672\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"335\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ab8dd4f4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxchTTxReJibRqtQuvW4r1DY37RyWfUh0MLe2MqkpsBCSNsf8pYRc7B5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但就是这样一张5美元的病理图，被AI彻底改变了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI把它翻译成了昂贵的、稀缺的、过去根本无法规模化的mIF免疫图像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当这种翻译被执行在14256名患者身上，形成近30万张虚拟免疫图谱之后，一个从未出现过的「虚拟人群」被点亮了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，癌症免疫研究第一次摆脱了样本之痛，有机会去回答那些之前无法回答的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也意味着，医学的尺度正悄悄发生偏移。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">5美元切片的逆袭</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当外界把癌症免疫研究和「昂贵」、「稀缺」画上等号时，GigaTIME却用最朴素、最廉价的切片打开了一条全新的通道。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169367\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8147622427253371\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1409\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1409\" data-height=\"1148\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"458\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac7f22f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxic7eLyqnUYk8lZo9kjicJx8m9ib4OAYojgVT46LR8eOiazOib12hCTHghQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">传统的multiplex immunofluorescence (mIF)，每张切片动辄几千美元，耗时长、样本少 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就算是顶尖实验室，一年的产出也只能覆盖整体样本的极少部分。这就注定了，传统mIF无法大面积使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但医院每天产生的H&amp;E染色切片，每张只要5～10美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">几十年来，它只被当做「常规诊断工具」，没有人会把它和「高维免疫图谱」联想在一起。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME改变了这一点。它通过跨模态学习，把H&amp;E里的形态特征翻译成mIF中的21个蛋白通道，让本来昂贵、稀缺、无法规模化的免疫信息，复制到每一张普通切片上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169365\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1426269137792102\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1241\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1241\" data-height=\"1418\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"642\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b09db82c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtx4WiccoZN2Uf9icJOSlUzds1n8hjibibyuDmSgNuW7wDI5I6m1ZFUTzLP6Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">A–B展示GigaTIME在结构一致性与信号一致性上均显著优于CycleGAN；C展示虚拟mIF与真实mIF的强相关性（以 DAPI、CK、CD68、CD4为例）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不是的小把戏，而是「结构性翻译」：细胞核、细胞质、结构纹理里潜藏的信号，重建成免疫空间里的真实表达。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就是为什么微软CEO会在X上亲自强调：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI正在让我们以前看不见的免疫信息，变得触手可及。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它向世界证明证明：癌症研究最贵的那部分，可以从最便宜的部分中「翻译」出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而当这种翻译被执行成规模时，一个全新的研究世界才开始展开。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">分析14256名癌症患者后，打开新世界的大门</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME把H&amp;E翻译成mIF后，发现了一个前所未有的研究窗口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去，受限于成本和样本量，免疫微环境（TIME）往往只能在几十例、最多上百例病例中观察。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而这一次，研究团队把模型应用在14256名癌症患者身上，横跨24种癌症、306个亚型，最终生成了299376张虚拟mIF图像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些病例来自Providence的真实世界临床医疗体系，横跨51家医院，上千家诊所。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这使GigaTIME的训练与验证扎根现实的土壤，而不是实验室的无菌环境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169363\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5304347826086957\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"920\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1265\" data-height=\"1518\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxm4dyqThAmW3Mo7gDbK8ibV53gf2MKicWsPqLjwz9feuYWVicscEvn1fTw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"920.6138790035587\" data-cropy2=\"488.4430604982207\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"298\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60707cdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxVeibDUpth5XOmL8Sdef0CBtXBiayoPI3Eo38IwDoQWewBnQtkeb3zfQQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">GigaTIME的整体研究框架。展示了14,000+患者规模的真实世界数据，H&amp;E→虚拟mIF的翻译流程，以及三大下游任务（生物标志物关联、患者分层、TCGA 验证）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">积累十年的数据，一次就被赶超。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这份虚拟人群带来的第一个成果，是规模化的生物标志物关联图谱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者在其中识别出1234个统计学显著的蛋白质–生物标志物关联。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169366\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7960474308300395\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1265\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1265\" data-height=\"1518\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxm4dyqThAmW3Mo7gDbK8ibV53gf2MKicWsPqLjwz9feuYWVicscEvn1fTw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1265\" data-cropy1=\"510.9519572953737\" data-cropy2=\"1517.099644128114\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"447\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9f66fce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtx1WOyib9GxAfRdJaqd0DdPovO1Q3vD16zukf7hgaPVcVULJapvaHeg1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">跨癌种的TIME免疫光谱图。展示不同癌种在21个蛋白通道上的免疫激活差异，涵盖增殖、免疫检查点、上皮–间质等功能类别。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中既包括已有文献支持的模式，例如MSI高、TMB高通常伴随TIME相关通道的升高 ；也出现了一些跨癌种的新型关联，例如与KRAS、KMT2D等驱动突变之间的免疫链接 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更重要的是，这个虚拟人群并非闭门造车。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队把GigaTIME生成的虚拟mIF与TCGA 10200名患者的数据进行了对照 ，得到了r =0.88的跨数据集一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169369\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1707988980716253\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"363\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1265\" data-height=\"1518\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxm4dyqThAmW3Mo7gDbK8ibV53gf2MKicWsPqLjwz9feuYWVicscEvn1fTw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"902.6067615658363\" data-cropx2=\"1265\" data-cropy1=\"72.02846975088968\" data-cropy2=\"497.4466192170819\" data-backw=\"161\" data-backh=\"188\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dcd6564d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxAc77QHtR4umVicYh8wGBlEfF7GkMSichKyvtqLGZMiaFwAPHg5Bafho8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Providence vs TCGA的虚拟mIF一致性</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着，无论是人群分布、癌种构成还是组织来源完全不同， GigaTIME的免疫翻译都保持了高度稳健。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">微软研究院将这项工作定义为：全球首个基于空间蛋白质组学的population-scaleTIME研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去，由于mIF稀缺，这类分析大多是理论上存在，如今，GigaTIME把事实摆在我们眼前。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">免疫能不能预测疾病？虚拟人群给出答案</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">接下来的工作，就是验证：这些被AI翻译出来的免疫信息，能不能用来判断疾病？能不能用于临床指导？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">答案比预期更大胆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队对近30万张虚拟mIF做了关联分析，发现了 1234项统计学显著的蛋白质–生物标志物关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169371\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3782805429864253\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1105\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1105\" data-height=\"1536\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxicZHzOa2iakLB7iapiaBsK9ulK1Rena1XUYPImvyDodNKwUqsccicUIumxw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1105\" data-cropy2=\"418.7989323843417\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"213\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=64748c90&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxUQb4UPicD1PIicIw1PyxkLTQ4pAEauacAiaWqMWLm36nlEv2Sgpz1UrMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些关系横跨跨癌种、癌种内部和亚型内三个层级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中既有文献验证的模式，例如MSI-H/TMB-H通常伴随 CD138、CD4等免疫相关通道普遍上调；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也出现了过去因样本量不足而无法观察到的新人群特征，例如KRAS、KMT2D等驱动突变与免疫活化之间的全局关联。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169373\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6714932126696832\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1105\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1105\" data-height=\"1536\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxicZHzOa2iakLB7iapiaBsK9ulK1Rena1XUYPImvyDodNKwUqsccicUIumxw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1105\" data-cropy1=\"426.6637010676157\" data-cropy2=\"1167.9181494661923\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"377\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a5eda7be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxg0rGTjBicib6JSJRHv4Mu9icsQStkaJ5aw1xAFgpaZO51I1iaPWA5Qh5SA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">虚拟 mIF × 生物标志物的关联矩阵</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是我们第一次在真实人群尺度上看到癌症免疫的因果纹理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队进一步提出问题：如果把21个虚拟mIF通道组合成一个整体特征，能否用于区分患者的生存风险？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">答案是肯定的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169370\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0477489768076398\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1466\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1466\" data-height=\"1536\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"589\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a9cf9f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtx3lmvfPjicUqKC2BCvGJnYPIZGgV6Cb84iaCyyIhbYWEyQfvCP6BIRhfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">虚拟mIF的生存分层能力。A–C展示虚拟mIF与病理分期的相关性；D–F显示CD3、CD8与GigaTIME signature在pan-cancer、肺癌、脑癌中的生存分层表现；G则给出不同蛋白通道对生存预测的重要性排序。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">pan-cancer层面，GigaTIME signature能明显区分生存曲线；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在肺癌和脑癌中，也呈现稳定的分层能力；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虚拟 CD3、虚拟 CD8 的预测效果，与真实CD3/CD8在文献中的表现高度一致。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">综合21通道的signature性能更优</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI翻译出来的免疫图谱不仅「像真的」，而且「能像真的一样用」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">免疫微环境真正难的一点，在于它是一个复杂的「空间结构问题」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169372\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32760180995475113\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1105\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1105\" data-height=\"1536\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxicZHzOa2iakLB7iapiaBsK9ulK1Rena1XUYPImvyDodNKwUqsccicUIumxw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1105\" data-cropy1=\"1173.8167259786478\" data-cropy2=\"1535.5960854092527\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"184\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0284c58a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxIaG5ia7GtHwCW0QBBAPDeo8TCicO16ZBWgHGfgfXsRhUia8ROcd5PhWwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">虚拟mIF的空间激活图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这类「免疫模式的合取与并集」在过去只能靠假设推测，现在在虚拟人群中可以直接验证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME让免疫微环境的「几何学」第一次能被系统分析。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">GigaTIME学到的不只技巧，还有语言本身</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真正让人相信它的，从来不是它预测得多么准确，而是「它是怎么学会这些的？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME的可信度，其实在它诞生的那一刻就已经定下来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">mIF价格高昂，一张几千美元，做研究就像是在烧钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">H&amp;E则完全相反，5~10美元一张，全球各地都在用它生成、扫描、存档。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME，把这两种世界接在了一起。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它从4千万个细胞级别、逐一对应的H&amp;E和mIF中学会了它们之间的语言关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更关键的是，当模型离开训练它的那套数据，被放到一个不同医院体系、不同样本来源的人群上时，依旧能行为稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505169374\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"576\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1946fd94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2dficI3E6yMUYT3mTJVuwtxXKIBcVru0AvQxGLM0ib7udxEwhsjhugOJ0tvJT0n0rdr7lg6mn3f84Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">往前走一步，很容易就能发现GigaTIME是站在巨人的肩膀上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">微软此前的GigaPath已经证明，H&amp;E里藏着极其丰富的结构信号。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GigaTIME只是进一步把这种结构翻译成免疫，把只有实验才能看到的东西，放在我们眼前。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也正因如此，前面那些大规模关联、生存分层、空间结构的发现，才不是模型的幻觉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们之所以可信，是因为模型从第一天起就站在真实世界的对照数据上，并不断在独立人群上被验证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你会感觉它不是「猜得对」，而是真的「听得懂」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从一张H&amp;E切片开始，GigaTIME推开了一扇没人想过的门：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">learning the language of patients.</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">意思是，医学终于有机会，把看得见的东西，延伸成真正能读懂病人的语言。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不是终点，更像是虚拟患者时代的第一块基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当免疫图谱能在几十万人的尺度上重建，未来关于疾病的预测、治疗反应的推演，可能都不止停留在猜测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，GigaTIME已在Foundry Labs与HuggingFace全量开源，这意味着它的优势不再属于少数团队，而将成为整个医学界都能继续构建的基础能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">新的故事，也许就会从这里开始。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/satyanadella/status/1998424249611211263\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/satyanadella/status/1998424249611211263</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/gigatime-scaling-tumor-microenvironment-modeling-using-virtual-population-generated-by-multimodal-ai/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/gigatime-scaling-tumor-microenvironment-modeling-using-virtual-population-generated-by-multimodal-ai/</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(25)01312-1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(25)01312-1</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "微软 GigaTIME 项目利用 AI 将廉价 H&E 病理切片转化为昂贵的免疫荧光图谱，首次实现癌症免疫微环境的人群尺度重建，为癌症研究带来突破性进展。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "微软 GigaTIME 项目利用 AI 将廉价 H&E 病理切片转化为昂贵的免疫荧光图谱，首次实现癌症免疫微环境的人群尺度重建，为癌症研究带来突破性进展。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了微软 GigaTIME 项目在癌症免疫研究领域的创新成果。该项目利用 AI 技术，能够将传统医院中廉价（5 美元）的 H&E 染色切片“翻译”成高昂且稀缺的 mIF 免疫图谱。通过这种跨模态学习，GigaTIME 将 H&E 中的形态特征映射为 mIF 中的 21 个蛋白通道，实现了对 14256 名患者、近 30 万张虚拟免疫图谱的生成，构建了一个前所未有的“虚拟人群”。这一突破性进展，不仅打破了传统癌症免疫研究中样本稀缺、成本高昂的限制，首次实现了人群尺度的肿瘤免疫微环境（TIME）研究，还通过大规模数据分析识别出 1234 个统计学显著的蛋白质-生物标志物关联，并验证了虚拟 mIF 在患者生存风险预测方面的能力，展现了 AI 在医学诊断和研究中的巨大潜力。文章强调 GigaTIME 并非简单技巧，而是通过学习数据本身的语言，在真实世界数据中得到验证，并已开源，有望成为医学界构建未来研究的基础工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GigaTIME 通过 AI 将廉价 H&E 切片转化为高维 mIF 免疫图谱，突破传统研究限制。",
      "explanation": "将每张仅需 5-10 美元的 H&E 切片，通过跨模态学习技术，翻译成昂贵稀缺的 mIF 图像，解决了传统研究中 mIF 样本获取难、成本高的痛点，实现免疫信息的大规模复制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "首次在人群尺度重建肿瘤免疫微环境（TIME），赋能癌症研究新范式。",
      "explanation": "通过分析 14256 名癌症患者，生成近 30 万张虚拟 mIF 图像，构建了全球首个基于空间蛋白质组学的 population-scale TIME 研究，揭示了前所未有的生物标志物关联和免疫图谱。"
    },
    {
      "point": "虚拟免疫图谱在生物标志物关联和患者生存预测方面展现出高度有效性。",
      "explanation": "GigaTIME 发现 1234 个统计学显著的蛋白质-生物标志物关联，并能有效区分患者生存风险，其虚拟 CD3、虚拟 CD8 预测效果与真实文献一致，证实了 AI 翻译信息的临床指导价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GigaTIME 学习了生物医学图像的“语言”，其成果基于真实数据并已开源。",
      "explanation": "模型从 4 千万个细胞级别的 H&E 和 mIF 数据中学习到内在联系，并在独立人群中得到验证，确保其稳健性和可信度。开源将加速医学界在该领域的探索和应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 把它翻译成了昂贵的、稀缺的、过去根本无法规模化的 mIF 免疫图像。",
    "癌症免疫研究第一次摆脱了样本之痛，有机会去回答那些之前无法回答的问题。",
    "AI 正在让我们以前看不见的免疫信息，变得触手可及。",
    "GigaTIME 让免疫微环境的「几何学」第一次能被系统分析。",
    "GigaTIME 推开了一扇没人想过的门：learning the language of patients。"
  ],
